last_episode_to_air.name: Banana Quest
last_episode_to_air.overview: Thinking Nesmith is ill, Sheen, Doppy and Aseefa go on a harrowing quest to find the only thing that can cure him: a banana.

name: Planet Sheen
overview: Jimmy Neutron's goofy pal, Sheen Estevez accidentally gets himself sent to another planet, millions of light-years from Earth.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview:
Sheen launches himself into outer space and crash lands on the planet Zeenu.

The Emperor and his daughter Oom takes an instant liking to Sheen but the Supreme Royal Adviser Dorkus wants to get rid of him after he destroys his house and usurps his influence over the Emperor.

In the meantime Sheen meets Mr. Nesmith, a lost space monkey from Earth and a native Zeenuian Sheen takes a liking to, Aseefa.

episodes.name: Is This Cute?
episodes.overview: The Emperor hires a tutor for Sheen to prepare him for a visit from Boh-Rok the Destroyer.

episodes.name: The Boy Next Dorkus
episodes.overview: Sheen moves across the street from Dorkus.

episodes.name: What's Up, Chock?
episodes.overview: When Aseefa's pet Chocktow goes missing, Sheen volunteers himself, Nesmith and Doppy to help her find him.

episodes.name: Joust Friends
episodes.overview: Princess Oom forces Sheen to face her ex-boyfriend in a battle for her affections, much to the reluctance of Sheen.

episodes.name: Keeping Up With the Gronzes
episodes.overview: After Sheen entertains the Emperor with his amazing joint cracking ability, he convinces the Emperor to record his “amazing” achievements. In a fit of jealousy, Dorkus enlists the help of the Gronze brothers who accepts Sheen's challenge of being the best.

episodes.name: Torzilla
episodes.overview: When Sheen grows tired of Zeenuian food, he searches out a lost crumb of tortilla from his spaceship. He plants it in the ground in hopes of growing some Earth food, but thanks to Dorkus, things go awry.

episodes.name: Thanksgetting
episodes.overview: When Sheen experiences a Zeenu holiday, he regales the Zeenuians of tales of Earth holidays and convinces them to celebrate Thanksgetting which entails Sheen receiving gifts.

episodes.name: There's Something About Scary
episodes.overview: After Princess Oom is scared by Aseefa's warrior face, she convinces the Emperor to lock up all the citizens with “scary” faces, but Sheen must step in.

episodes.name: Act I, Sheen I
episodes.overview: After the Emperor refuses to give out an acting award because Zeenuians acting is terrible, Sheen brags about how good of a tree actor he is. Dorkus overhears Sheen and creates a play where the final act will eliminate Sheen permanently.

episodes.name: Money Suits Sheen
episodes.overview: After Sheen sees the Emperor's money suit, he decides he must make some cash to obtain his own but realizes it comes at a high cost.

episodes.name: Cutting the Ultra-Cord
episodes.overview: Sheen realizes he no longer needs Ultra Lord.

episodes.name: Trial By Jerry
episodes.overview: After the Emperor's pet, Beebaw, goes missing and Nesmith is accused, Sheen convinces the Emperor to hold a trial.

episodes.name: Chock Around the Clock
episodes.overview: While pet-sitting, Sheen accidentally gets Aseefa's pet Chocktow caught by Animal Control and has to rescue him before she returns.

episodes.name: The Oomlick Maneuver
episodes.overview: In an attempt to stop Princess Oom from liking and licking him, Sheen tries to get her back together with her ex-boyfriend.

episodes.name: To Chill A Mocking Blurg
episodes.overview: The Emperor's Royal Ball of Compliments quickly turns into a Hall of Insults as Sheen and his friends are plagued by a flock of bird-like, rowdy, mocking blurgs.

episodes.name: Now You Sheen It
episodes.overview: Sheen puts on a magic show that actually makes people disappear.

episodes.name: Desperate Houseguests
episodes.overview: Sheen helps Doppy's parents rid their house of an unwanted guest.

episodes.name: Nesvidanya
episodes.overview: Sheen has to rescue Nesmith from a mythical white-haired creature, the Boopenfoofer.

episodes.name: ExpreSheenism
episodes.overview: Sheen's starts a new art movement only to have it take over his life.

episodes.name: Gotta Go
episodes.overview: Sheen has to "go" but he doesn't want Aseefa to know.

episodes.name: Sheen Racer
episodes.overview: Sheen enters a flying bug saucer race.

episodes.name: QuaranSheen
episodes.overview: To avoid Oom's advances, Sheen fakes an illness called "dance fever" that actually starts spreading to other Zeenuians.

episodes.name: Washing My Sheen
episodes.overview: Sheen vows to never bathe again and accidentally attracts a horde of destructive, filth-loving beasts.

episodes.name: Stuck in the Riddle with You
episodes.overview: Sheen has to use his matchless wit to rid Zeenu and save his friends from a carnivorous, pretentious plant called the Dentamental.

episodes.name: He Went Hataway
episodes.overview: Sheen uses his master detective skills to find Nesmith's missing hat.

episodes.name: Tongue-Tied
episodes.overview: Sheen gets stuck to Oom's tongue and must find a way to free himself.

episodes.name: A Well Oiled Fighting Ma-Sheen
episodes.overview: Sheen must train the Emperor's Guard to prepare for emergence of a legendary beast, the Londar.

episodes.name: Dorkus in Chains
episodes.overview: Accidentally chained to each other, Sheen and Dorkus are trapped underground and must work together to find a way out.

episodes.name: Ooze on First
episodes.overview: Sheen teaches Zeenu his version of baseball.

episodes.name: Monster-Fighting Combat Strike Force
episodes.overview: Doppy's parents fear their son is becoming too courageous when he and Sheen form the Monster-Fighting Combat Strike Force.

episodes.name: Sheen Says
episodes.overview: Chaos ensues when the Emperor leaves town and puts Sheen in charge of the kingdom.

episodes.name: Hippocratic Oaf
episodes.overview: Sheen becomes a doctor and sets up a clinic in Zeenu.

episodes.name: Scape Doat
episodes.overview: Sheen blames Doppy's new pet for breaking his figurine collection.

episodes.name: Haute CuiSheen
episodes.overview: Sheen starts an Earth food restaurant.

episodes.name: Raging Belle
episodes.overview: Sheen helps Aseefa get through her one night of Tahlak Pow where she turns into a vicious, rampaging beast.

episodes.name: Breath Wish
episodes.overview: Sheen tries to keep Zeenu safe from Baby Arms Banarog, a desperado with evil breath.

episodes.name: Sheen for a Day
episodes.overview: Sheen accidentally gives Princess Oom the most important part of his rocket ship and has to find a way to get it back.

episodes.name: Well Bread Man
episodes.overview: Seeing an opportunity to destroy Sheen, Dorkus volunteers to train him for the "Manhood Trial by Fire."

episodes.name: Nesmith is Spoken For
episodes.overview: When Nesmith loses his ability to speak, Sheen must save the planet using the awesome power of ventriloquism.

episodes.name: Feeling Roovy
episodes.overview: Sheen helps Aseefa get her Roove back.

episodes.name: Shave the Last Dance for Me
episodes.overview: In order to help Aseefa, Sheen purchases a black market mustache and must deal with the consequences when it gets out of control.

episodes.name: Berry Big Trouble
episodes.overview: Sheen eats a berry that makes him huge and hazardous.

episodes.name: MetamorphoSheen
episodes.overview: Sheen has to figure out a way to lead the Celebration of Legs Parade despite the fact that he's turning into an eel.

episodes.name: MisSheen Impossible
episodes.overview: Sheen and Nesmith rescue Doppy from a group of gloop thieves, the Gashlubbs.

episodes.name: Blunderlings
episodes.overview: To improve Zeenu's government, Sheen introduces the concept of Clown College.

episodes.name: Dawn of the Wedge
episodes.overview: Zeenu is attacked a swarm of wedgie-giving barbarians and it's up to Sheen to stop them.

episodes.name: Nightmare Sheenario
episodes.overview: After accidentally waking the Empress up during her year-long beauty sleep, Sheen must help her fall back asleep before she makes everyone's lives miserable.

episodes.name: Drak-a-Bye-Baby
episodes.overview: In order to keep his new baby Drakbog, Sheen has to civilize it using parenting tips from Dorkus.

episodes.name: Banana Quest
episodes.overview: Thinking Nesmith is ill, Sheen, Doppy and Aseefa go on a harrowing quest to find the only thing that can cure him: a banana.
